data.description: Your dream home awaits! This charming Cape Cod style residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Three spacious bedrooms and 2.5 well appointed bathrooms, this two story gem is perfect for families of all sizes. Step inside and discover the heart of this home, a cozy living room, featuring a wood burning fireplace. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining space and kitchen. Meal prep is a breeze in  this large kitchen with abundant storage space, modern appliances provide an ideal environment for culinary creativity. One of the highlights of this property is location with Patriot Estates which offers fantastic community amenities. Enjoy sunny days at the community pool, stay active on the basketball court or let the kids play on the well maintained playgrounds. Additionally, the expansive green space is perfect for peaceful walk or tossing a ball. Discover more than just a house, make this your home today.
